# HTML Slides as Code

Simple HTML presentations with version control.

## Structure
```
src/
├── slides/     # HTML slides (slide-XX.html)
└── assets/     # Styles (base.css) and images
scripts/        # build.sh, pdf.sh
dist/           # Generated files (gitignored)
```

## Core Rules
- All slides in `src/slides/`
- Name format: `slide-XX.html` (01-99)
- Styles: base.css + scoped in slides
- 16:9 ratio (1280x720px)
- Scripts run from root
- PDF: one slide per page

## Best Practices
- Semantic HTML5
- Modern CSS, no external deps
- Optimize images
- Accessible content
- Clean commits 